description:
Parables of Jesus | Trailer | Clarence Mitchell | Jack Gwynne

Here are seven short dramas portraying the parables of Jesus through the lens of Bible times. They are stories that never grow old!  In these videos you will see the Bible come alive, understand the customs and culture behind the parables, and feel the impact of Jesus' message.  The seven stories are as follows:
The Good Samaritan
The Unmerciful Servant
The Treasure and the Pearl
The Lost Son
The Midnight Visitor
The Dinner
The Manager.  A wonderful resource for Bible study, small groups and Sunday school.

Producer: International Media Ministries
Starring: Christopher Gornold-Smith
